===Etymology===
Borrowed from {{bor|en|ota|حرم|tr=harem}} {{cog|tr|harem}}, from {{der|en|ar|حَرَم||something prohibited; sanctuary, women}}; and later also from {{m|ar|حَرِيم}} with same meaning, both from {{m|ar|حَرُمَ||be forbidden or unlawful}}.

